{"tid":2014473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"應該用咩有效方法教學歷低嘅老豆老母用smartphone?","createTime":"2020-05-13T05:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T06:14:00.000Z","uid":102343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"216bf01d3e8ee94fc1df332006d62f06a2521360","tid":2014473,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得老一輩學用smartphone 嘅方式係死記果粒制有咩用，即使有文字描述佢好多時都唔明，而且佢地唔知啲icon代表啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如唔知全螢幕係咩icon<br />\n<br />\n而我地後生嘅主要係辨認icon、文字描述加user experience from pc or other phone、咩都禁落去睇下黎試<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩方法係最有效教佢地用smartphone用到好似我地咁?<br />\n有冇巴絲可以分享下經驗或者資源e.g) icon表? 流程圖?<br />\n<br />\n最低限度想教佢用打/聽電話、相機、whatsapp、睇新聞、聽歌、YouTube 、地圖、交通工具app<br />\n<br />\n最理想係令佢可以自學同自己摸索點download app同自己學點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n而家教左佢用rthk睇新聞<br />\n打/聽電話<br />\n影相<br />\n睇媒體庫嘅相/片<br />\n但而家佢都唔係好熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d055942fc80b74d2896ef4eb69f1a84afc39ee45","tid":2014473,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"留名等睇高手教路"},{"pid":"844c4bc87a9f33d9b213709918e332265d369882","tid":2014473,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"你老豆老母黃定藍??"},{"pid":"27867fe08d8ce9a0f425b0fa3c5d86967810c7ab","tid":2014473,"uid":335303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"有心就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ecca96570bf90eb213b11c9891c43003fcf6f5","tid":2014473,"uid":12254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"教佢上pornhub"},{"pid":"cdd50f667fc143b33c7b1b576c19f4eeb6191a40","tid":2014473,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-